videos.headline: Gus Ragland lofts his second TD pass of the day
videos.description: Miami (OH)'s Gus Ragland tosses a pass to Jack Sorenson for a 26-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Doege tosses 7-yard TD  pass
videos.description: Jarret Doege lofts a 7-yard pass to Quinton Morris for a Bowling Green touchdown.

videos.headline: Bowling Green' Sawmiller catches a tip-drill TD to end game
videos.description: Grant Loy throws up a prayer that is caught off the tip by Justin Sawmiller for a 40-yard touchdown to end Bowling Green's loss to Miami (OH).
